title: With 50m followers, Taylor Swift crowned as Insta queen
text:
*Washington, Oct. 9(ANI): Not only she rules hearts, but with her 50 million followers, Taylor Swift is ruling Instagram as well.*
Washington, Oct. 9(ANI): Not only she rules hearts, but with her 50 million followers, Taylor Swift is ruling Instagram as well. The 25-year-old songstress took to Instagram to thank all of her fans and wrote, "50 million followers! Thanks so much guys. I'm pretty sure this is just because I have cute cats though," reports E! Online. The 'Bad Blood' hit-maker now clocks in at a fan base higher than Beyonce and Kim Kardashian , who have 47.5 and 48.4 million followers each, respectively. (ANI) Â»
